quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,"Sinam taamak tatrusseemik cisab keenik edde aban uddur (wakti) keenih xayyooweh, usun (koros kinnuk) ken qambaltaamak garcit anuk, ken kah seecaanamat derre cabak"
  21,2,"Yalli qusbuk keenil oobisaah yamaate Qhuraanay kas keenih yacee mayan, usuk keenil oobe kaa tekkek usun digir kee anqasak sa kaa kah ankacsaanam malon"
  21,3,"Qhuraanak sorkocobbaxitte keenik garcii kee agxet anuk, daalimiinih yan mari (koros kinnuk) garay qellisak, ama Mucammad sin innah yan seehadaytu akke waytek kalah kah yanim malik usuk Qhuraanak luk yemeetem baabak isin baabâ fanah mannal tamaateeniih katattan, isin baab kinnim kaak abaluk iyyen"
  21,4,"Nabii keenik iyyeh; yi-Rabbi qaran kee baaxól maxcók ixxicci iyyaanam yaaxigeh, kaadu Usuk sin maxcooca yaabbi, sin abtoota yaaxigi"
  21,5,"Wonna hinnay wohuk kalah koros Qhuraan tengeddeh, usuk tengeggele soonoonâ kal Yallih yab hinna iyyen, wonna hinnay Mucammad diraabah kaa ginnaasitê kal usuk wacyi hinna iyyen, wonna hinnay usuk (Mucammad kinnuk) gad-abé iyyen, toysa usuk kaa nummasnam nek faxek astá neh baahay, dumi farmoytit tambullee astooti luk kah temeete innah"
  21,6,Makki korosuk naharat hebeltô magaalah maray esseren astooti kah baaheeni maamaninnaay nanu ken bayisnehik usun esseran astooti keenih bahnek ama koros maay aaminele
  21,7,"Kaadu Nabii Mucammadow kok naharat hebeltô farmoyta seehadâ fanah maruubinnino seehadak wacyi elle oobisne labhay ken fanah rubne akke waytek, toysa makkķki korosey siinik duma kitab elle oobe marak ixxiga-le mara essera isin woh aaxigewaa mara tekkeenik"
  21,8,"Kaadu woo farmoytiitiy kok duma seehadâ fanah rubne xagar maaqó kak faxewaah akmewaa mara ken maabinninooy seehadah innaah akamuk aaqabuk sugen, kaadu usun addunyal rabewaah waara marah masuginnon"
  21,9,"Tohuk lakat ambiyah xagana duudusneh ken kee Ni naqoosak keenil yeemene marak ninnih fanna mara digaalak naggosnaamal, tokkel ken kee moominiinik ken kataate mara naggosneh, kaadu koroosannuu kee umaanet caddok tatre mara finqisneh"
  21,10,"Nummah Qhuraan kitaabay addunyaa kee akeeral nabna siinik edde tani siinih oobisnek, elle makas-kassowtaanaa"
  21,11,Kaadu makina magaalah mara finqisneeh koroosannut isi nafsi yudlumeh suge marak !kaadu keenik lakat aka mara ginne keenik kalah
  21,12,"Tokkel Ni-gibdi digaalá sinnil oobah yablen waqdi, usun too waqdi teetik kudeenih teetik yassaqqoonuwaanam akkaluk"
  21,13,"Too waqdi Malayka keenik ittah: makudinay edde sugten temqoo kee sinni dabooqah gaca sin addunyak tul esserimtaanamkeh"
  21,14,Koros nee gee finqaaw! Diggah nanu ninni nafsi koroosannut yudlume marah sugne itta
  21,15,"Tokkel too maxcol sinni abaaraanaah, tet gacan- gacsaanamak makatinnon, yirgiqeeniih orbisen buqreh (darqi kinnuk) inna ken abba haynam fanah, rabeeh bargeeh angoyyi sinni mara ken abne"
  21,16,"Kaadu qaran kee baaxooy, ken nammayih fanal tanim digirih magininnino"
  21,17,"Barraa kee xaylo haysitnam fannaamal Ninni garik ken haysitak nen, Nanu woh abá hinnino woh Nee ceele waytaamih sabbatah"
  21,18,"Wonna hinnay, cakki deedalal qambisnaah kaa baysaah usuk too waqdi kataah bayah, korosey akeeral gibdi digaala liton sin Rabbi ceele waytaamat kaa weelossaanamih sabbatah"
  21,19,"Kaadu Qaranwaa kee baaxól tanim inkih Yalli-le, kaadu Malaykak Kay xaqul yan mari Kay qibaadak makaxxa-mariinitaay, mataqba (manakura)"
  21,20,"Usun (malayka kinnuk) baraay, laqó Yalla saytunnoysaanaah mataqbaanaay mataanan"
  21,21,Hinnak ama koros tu-xiqe wayta Yallitte baaxok haysittaah is rabtem taynuwweeh ugussaa? Aleey muugussa
  21,22,"Qaranwaa kee baaxól Yallak kalah yallitte aninnay, ken nammay bayak yen, tokkel Qarshi Rabbi usun Ķaa edde weelossu haanamak saytunih"
  21,23,"Yalli isi ginok abeh yaniimik messerima, abeenimik usun esserimaanâ kal"
  21,24,"Hinnak A-koros Yallak kalah Yallitte haysittee? Nabiyow ittaanamal sumaq baaha keenik ixxic, A-yolluk yan kitaabaay (Qhuraan kinnuk), yok duma Yallih farmoytiitil obte kitoobal Yallat agleyta haanamih sumaq mayanak, Wonna hinnay keenik maggo mari cakki mayaaxiga usun cakkit derre cabaanaah kaa yangaddeenih ikkal"
  21,25,"Nabiyow kok duma hebeltô farmoyta maruubinnino farmoytiitik, wacyi kaal oobisna nee akke waytek, diggah yok-sa Qibaada cakkisita Yalli aneewaamal, toysa yoo inkittoysaay Qibaada yoh caglisa iyyaanamal ken rubne"
  21,26,"Koros Racmaan kinni Rabbi xaylo haysite itte, Malayka Kay say-xayló axcuk, Yalli tohuk saytunnooweh, wonna hinna usun (Malayka kinnuk) Yallih naqoosay Yalli yessekexxee kinni"
  21,27,"Usun (malayka kinnuk) Yallak maxcó mayaakumaanaay, usun Kay amril taamitan"
  21,28,"Malaykâ taamoomik hebeltô taama matakka, abeenim kee aboonuwaanam inkih Yalli keenik yaaxige Ķaa akke waytek, kaadu Qhiyaamah ayró shafaaqatta numuh mayakkan Yalli shafaaqattat kak leedaah kah oggola mara (moominiin kinnuk) akke waytek, kaadu usun Kay meesih Kay amri cinaanamak cibbarsimaah meesita mara kinnon"